{"prompt": "Design an engaging platform for an independent music label. The aesthetic should incorporate a vibrant electric purple.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Electric Soundwave Records</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #4b0082; /* Electric Purple */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n        }\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 40px 20px;\n        }\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #4b0082, #9400d3); /* Electric Purple to Lighter Purple */\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n        nav ul {\n            list-style: none;\n            padding: 0;\n            margin: 20px 0 0 0;\n        }\n        nav ul li {\n            display: inline;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n        }\n        nav ul li a {\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        nav ul li a:hover {\n            color: #d8bfd8; /* Thistle - a lighter, complementary shade */\n        }\n        .hero {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 80px 20px;\n            background: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" viewBox=\"0 0 100 100\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\"><polygon points=\"0,0 100,0 100,100 0,100\" fill=\"rgba(75, 0, 130, 0.3)\" /></svg>') no-repeat center center;\n            background-size: cover;\n            border-bottom: 5px solid #9400d3;\n        }\n        .hero h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n        .artists, .releases, .contact {\n            padding: 60px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        h3 {\n            font-size: 2em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            border-bottom: 2px solid #9400d3;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n            display: inline-block;\n        }\n        .artist-grid, .release-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n        .artist-item, .release-item {\n            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\n            padding: 20px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n        .artist-item:hover, .release-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n        .artist-item img, .release-item img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 150px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 3px solid #9400d3;\n        }\n        .artist-item h4, .release-item h4 {\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n            color: #ffffff;\n        }\n        .artist-item p, .release-item p {\n            font-size: 0.95em;\n            line-height: 1.5;\n            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);\n        }\n        .contact-form {\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin: 30px auto;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n        .contact-form input[type=\"text\"],\n        .contact-form input[type=\"email\"],\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            width: calc(100% - 20px);\n            padding: 12px 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid #9400d3;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\n            color: #ffffff;\n            font-size: 1em;\n            transition: border-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .contact-form input[type=\"text\"]:focus,\n        .contact-form input[type=\"email\"]:focus,\n        .contact-form textarea:focus {\n            outline: none;\n            border-color: #d8bfd8;\n        }\n        .contact-form button {\n            background-color: #9400d3;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: #d8bfd8;\n            color: #4b0082;\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #300054; /* Darker Purple */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n        footer a {\n            color: #d8bfd8;\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n        .waveform {\n            position: absolute;\n            bottom: -50px;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100px;\n            background: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" viewBox=\"0 0 100 100\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\"><path d=\"M0 50 Q20 0, 40 50 T80 50 T100 50 L100 100 L0 100 Z\" fill=\"%239400d3\" opacity=\"0.7\"/></svg>');\n            background-size: cover;\n            z-index: 0;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Electric Soundwave Records</h1>\n            <nav>\n                <ul>\n                    <li><a href=\"#about\">About</a></li>\n                    <li><a href=\"#artists\">Artists</a></li>\n                    <li><a href=\"#releases\">Releases</a></li>\n                    <li><a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a></li>\n                </ul>\n            </nav>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"waveform\"></div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"about\" class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Unleash Your Sound</h2>\n            <p>We are a passionate independent music label dedicated to amplifying unique voices and groundbreaking sounds. From pulsating electronic beats to soulful melodies, we champion artists who dare to be different.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"artists\" class=\"container\">\n        <h3>Featured Artists</h3>\n        <div class=\"artist-grid\">\n            <div class=\"artist-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/250x150/9400d3/ffffff?text=Artist+1\" alt=\"Artist 1\">\n                <h4>Nova Pulse</h4>\n                <p>Electronic virtuoso crafting ethereal soundscapes.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"artist-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/250x150/9400d3/ffffff?text=Artist+2\" alt=\"Artist 2\">\n                <h4>Crimson Echoes</h4>\n                <p>Indie rock band with electrifying live performances.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"artist-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/250x150/9400d3/ffffff?text=Artist+3\" alt=\"Artist 3\">\n                <h4>Luna Cadence</h4>\n                <p>Singer-songwriter weaving poetic narratives with ambient tones.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"artist-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/250x150/9400d3/ffffff?text=Artist+4\" alt=\"Artist 4\">\n                <h4>Rhythm Syndicate</h4>\n                <p>Funk and soul collective bringing infectious grooves.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"releases\" class=\"container\">\n        <h3>Latest Releases</h3>\n        <div class=\"release-grid\">\n            <div class=\"release-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/250x150/4b0082/ffffff?text=Release+1\" alt=\"Release 1\">\n                <h4>Nova Pulse - Celestial Drift</h4>\n                <p>Immerse yourself in a journey of cosmic electronica.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"release-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/250x150/4b0082/ffffff?text=Release+2\" alt=\"Release 2\">\n                <h4>Crimson Echoes - Shattered Skies</h4>\n                <p>A powerful collection of anthemic rock tracks.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"release-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/250x150/4b0082/ffffff?text=Release+3\" alt=\"Release 3\">\n                <h4>Luna Cadence - Whispers in the Dark</h4>\n                <p>An intimate exploration of emotion and vulnerability.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\" class=\"container\">\n        <h3>Get In Touch</h3>\n        <div class=\"contact-form\">\n            <form action=\"#\" method=\"post\">\n                <input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                <textarea name=\"message\" rows=\"5\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" required></textarea>\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Electric Soundwave Records. All rights reserved.</p>\n            <p>Follow us on <a href=\"#\">SoundCloud</a> | <a href=\"#\">Bandcamp</a> | <a href=\"#\">Instagram</a></p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}